        <h3><b>Welcome to Mutual Risk Management Ltd.</b></h3>
        <p>Mutual Risk Management Ltd. (MRM) is a publicly traded
        risk management services organization, listed on the New
        York Stock Exchange under the symbol <a
        href="http://www.pcquote.com/cgi-bin/getquote.exe?TICKER=mm">&quot;MM&quot;</a>.
        Bermuda is the home of MRM and also home to about half
        the captive insurance companies in the world, as they
        enjoy a good geographical location, coupled with a stable
        economic climate.<br>
        <br>
        MRM is a leader in the dynamic Alternative Insurance
        Market which is one of the fastest growing segments of
        the insurance industry. MRM has an outstanding record of
        profitable growth, which is fee base driven and produces
        stability and predictability. Mutual Risk was recently
        included in Forbes Magazine's list of the &quot;100 Best
        Small Companies in the World,&quot; and its assets are
        now in excess of $1.3 billion. MRM has a small share of
        an enormous market and continues to acquire companies to
        expand service to our clients. MRM constantly reviews new
        market areas to respond to the changing needs of our
        clients.<br>
        <br>
        We invite you to browse through our Web page to discover
        our services and find out more about MRM. Please click
        the buttons above to explore more of the MRM Web site.<br>
        <br>
